\ncandidates with a mass in the range of 5-10 GeV, decaying into pairs of\nelectrons and positrons.\n  This thesis contributes to a broad spectrum of research for particle dark\nmatter on different levels, since we considered different types of signals,\nmultiple targets and different mass scales.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Nov 2022 21:24:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-02"}
