resulting kink wave\nis circularly polarised. These results may have implications for seismology of\nmagnetohydrodynamic waves in solar magnetic vortices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Dec 2022 09:19:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-14"}
